sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>(kube-rbac-proxy /<br/>Gateway API)
    participant KServeRouter as KServe Router
    participant HTTP as vllm-spyre HTTP API<br/>8000/TCP
    participant GRPC as vllm-spyre gRPC API<br/>8033/TCP (TGIS)
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine
    participant Spyre as IBM Spyre<br/>Accelerator
    participant S3 as Model Storage<br/>(S3 / PVC / HF)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Loading at Startup
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Engine->>S3: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / Bearer Token
        S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts
        Engine->>Spyre: Load model onto accelerator<br/>Hardware interface
        Spyre-->>Engine: Model ready
    end

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
        Ingress->>KServeRouter: Forward (auth validated)
        KServeRouter->>HTTP: HTTP/8000<br/>In-cluster (plaintext)
        HTTP->>Engine: Process inference request
        Engine->>Spyre: Execute on accelerator<br/>Hardware interface
        Spyre-->>Engine: Inference result
        Engine-->>HTTP: Completion response
        HTTP-->>KServeRouter: JSON response
        KServeRouter-->>Ingress: Forward response
        Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS
    end

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS Protocol)
    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Client->>Ingress: gRPC GenerationService<br/>TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
        Ingress->>KServeRouter: Forward (auth validated)
        KServeRouter->>GRPC: gRPC/8033<br/>In-cluster (plaintext)
        GRPC->>Engine: Process generation request
        Engine->>Spyre: Execute on accelerator<br/>Hardware interface
        Spyre-->>Engine: Inference result
        Engine-->>GRPC: Generation response
        GRPC-->>KServeRouter: gRPC response
        KServeRouter-->>Ingress: Forward response
        Ingress-->>Client: gRPC Response<br/>TLS
    end
